FaultTolerantResourceAdaptorContextImpl
public interface FaultTolerantResourceAdaptorContext<K extends java.io.Serializable,V extends java.io.Serializable>

Fault tolerant context for a FaultTolerantResourceAdaptor, gives access to replicated data and information of the SLEE cluster.

Author:
martins
